The '''Council of Higher Education''' ({{lang-tr|Yükseköğretim Kurulu}}, YÖK; also translated as ''Higher Education Board'') is responsible for the supervision of [[List of universities in Turkey|universities in Turkey]], in a capacity defined by articles 130 and 131 of the [[Turkish Constitution of 1982|1982 constitution]].
